public class NetscapeCertType
extends DERBitString
The NetscapeCertType object. 
    NetscapeCertType ::= BIT STRING {
         SSLClient               (0),
         SSLServer               (1),
         S/MIME                  (2),
         Object Signing          (3),
         Reserved                (4),
         SSL CA                  (5),
         S/MIME CA               (6),
         Object Signing CA       (7) }
